snippet.title: THE RUSH Stage 1
snippet.description:
Just a short video of my game's first stage (played on the default difficulty). It is intended to give a brief idea of what to expect. There is far more information written on the game's steam page. Sorry for the video quality.

P.S. PROTOSTAR scope creeped out of control given my limited game development skills, so THE RUSH has been a sort of compromise that incorporates many aspects from PROTOSTAR into a more feasible project for myself.
